page.title: 20Ecology
page.content: The{trees}in our block are mostly coniferous in the south east and decidious in the north west. The coniferous{trees}at Tentsmuir forest are Larch,Scotch pine and Silver fir.The{trees}that are at Scotscraig farm are Scots pine, Beach,Silver Birch, copper birch, Oak,Elms,Monkey puzzle,Chesnut,sweet chesnut,walnut and sequoia. The{animal}life in our block is very interesting there is a wide variety of animals.All the wild animals are found in the farm woods and in Tentsmuir forest.There are many wild{animals living in the forest: The rarest is the Red Squirrel and there are also the Roe Deer,the Brown Hare,the Hedgehog,the Pine Marten and many more.One of the sea creatures is the Common Seal.
